<!--
  Audita appcast — host this file at:
  https://headroomstudio.dev/audita/appcast.xml

  Audita is the renamed successor to Auris. The Auris appcast at
  /auris/appcast.xml is intentionally left in place so existing Auris
  installs continue to receive the final 1.3 update; new development
  ships exclusively via this feed.

  How to update for a new release:
  1. Run: make release  →  produces Audita.dmg
  2. Upload Audita.dmg to Cloudflare R2 as Audita-X.Y.dmg, copy the public URL
  3. Get the file size in bytes:  wc -c < Audita.dmg
  4. Sign the DMG with Sparkle:   .build/artifacts/sparkle/Sparkle/bin/sign_update Audita.dmg
     (this prints the edSignature value)
  5. Add a new <item> block at the top (keep old items for reference)
  6. Push to GitHub Pages — Sparkle clients re-fetch on their own schedule
-->
